name: Quantum Facilities
body:
# Welcome to **Quantum Facilities Mod** page!
### Quantum Facilities is now, maintained by @SiG-200 is a Japanese Java developer and anime/manga lover <3.
Feel free to explore this page, we don't have much things on it yet...

### What is Quantum Facilities Mod?
Quantum Facilities add a lot of machines, mobs, ores, resources and more to your game! As a industrial mod I wanna to make a lot of funny things and crazy things at all... xD.

### Can I support you?
Yes. You can support me giving tips and feedbacks in our github page ;), You can send me a email to make this mod better, if your collaboration is great, I'll make a special thing for you in the mod. Thanks A Lot, bye bye!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
